{"tid":1336513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"指紋 其實好容易隱藏","createTime":"2019-07-21T03:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:48:50.000Z","uid":215950,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84522d1098275c88fcf0834c3ece787ac9d318ae","tid":1336513,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"大家發夢個時都會係夢入面做好多野，而留低指紋係好危險，因為會比外星人捉走。<br />\n<br />\n睇戲見過騙徒去銀行做世界，唔洗戴手套都冇留底指紋，只要用膠水/白膠漿搽落手指頭，乾左就變成一層隱形既薄膜，唔會留底指紋，又唔容易甩，用完又好易捽走。<br />\n<br />\n戲入面既騙徒配合埋易容術，就更難搵到佢真正身份啦。"},{"pid":"973fd6da8b46026516b5712e28e1d538f7631d95","tid":1336513,"uid":73972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"呢d天氣好易溶又痴痴立立，透氣手套最方便"},{"pid":"fd36e777de348722134b630162aa12e4209c080b","tid":1336513,"uid":197640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"睇美劇見過條頸掛粒laser紅燈仔，cctv 即時影唔到人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3057fffd5c80b8791c18f65a4152c5f45d759f2c","tid":1336513,"uid":183386,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e47e069aec0d9f4916f25bba5f3222278a5b8c38","tid":1336513,"uid":201726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd36e777de348722134b630162aa12e4209c080b","tid":1336513,"uid":197640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"睇美劇見過條頸掛粒laser紅燈仔，cctv 即時影唔到人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"外國細力🤣🤣"},{"pid":"722ef5ba17de16898830f685a33d49af043a262a","tid":1336513,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47e069aec0d9f4916f25bba5f3222278a5b8c38","tid":1336513,"uid":201726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd36e777de348722134b630162aa12e4209c080b","tid":1336513,"uid":197640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T04:02:53.0